{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "E2E Test — Full Stack Real App Testing (Playwright + Fetch)",
  "description": "Setelah testcase document dibuat, LANGSUNG test backend API via Fetch MCP ke running server dan test frontend UI via Playwright MCP ke running app. Isi form, klik button, verifikasi data — screenshot SETIAP step. Generate report MD + HTML + JSON.",
  "version": "4",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileCreated",
    "patterns": [
      "reports/testcases/**/*-testcases.md"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Baca kiro/agents/e2e_test_agent.yaml dan kiro/rules/qa_planning_rules.md.\n\nTestcase document baru dibuat. Kamu HARUS LANGSUNG MENJALANKAN test ke RUNNING APPLICATION — backend API dan frontend UI. BUKAN menulis instruksi, tapi BENAR-BENAR EKSEKUSI.\n\n## PERSIAPAN\n\n1. Baca testcase document yang baru dibuat\n2. Baca unit test files di project (*_test.go, *.test.ts) sebagai referensi expected behavior\n3. Baca kiro/memory/api_contract.yaml untuk daftar endpoints\n4. Tentukan base URLs:\n   - Backend API: baca dari environment config atau default http://localhost:8080\n   - Frontend App: baca dari environment config atau default http://localhost:3000\n   - Swagger UI: http://localhost:8080/swagger/\n5. Buat folder: reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/screenshots/{feature}/ dan reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/captures/{feature}/\n\n## BAGIAN A: BACKEND API TEST — LANGSUNG HIT ENDPOINT PAKAI FETCH MCP\n\nUntuk SETIAP testcase bertipe API di testcase document, LANGSUNG panggil endpoint:\n\n### Flow Per API Testcase:\n\nStep 1 — Health Check:\n- Panggil fetch ke GET /health untuk pastikan server running\n- Simpan response ke {TC-ID}-step-1-response.json\n- Jika server tidak running, mark BLOCKED dan lanjut ke testcase berikutnya\n\nStep 2 — Eksekusi API Call:\n- Panggil fetch dengan method yang sesuai (GET/POST/PUT/PATCH/DELETE) ke endpoint yang ditest\n- Sertakan headers (Content-Type, Authorization jika perlu)\n- Sertakan request body sesuai testcase\n- Simpan request ke {TC-ID}-step-2-request.json (method, url, headers, body, timestamp)\n- Simpan response ke {TC-ID}-step-2-response.json (status, headers, body, duration_ms)\n\nStep 3 — Verifikasi Response:\n- Cek status code sesuai expected (200, 201, 400, 401, 404, dll)\n- Cek response body structure sesuai API contract\n- Simpan verification result ke {TC-ID}-step-3-verification.json\n\nStep 4 — Error Path (jika ada di testcase):\n- Panggil fetch dengan invalid data / tanpa auth / wrong method\n- Simpan request + response untuk setiap error scenario\n- Verifikasi error response format dan status code\n\n### Contoh Backend Test — Create Item:\n1. fetch POST /api/v1/items dengan body JSON data item baru\n2. Simpan request.json dan response.json\n3. Verifikasi response status 201 dan body berisi item yang dibuat\n4. fetch GET /api/v1/items/{id} untuk verifikasi data tersimpan\n5. Simpan response.json — verifikasi data match\n\n### Contoh Backend Test — Error Handling:\n1. fetch POST /api/v1/items dengan body KOSONG — verifikasi 400\n2. fetch GET /api/v1/items/nonexistent-id — verifikasi 404\n3. fetch tanpa Authorization header ke protected endpoint — verifikasi 401\n\n## BAGIAN B: FRONTEND UI TEST — LANGSUNG BUKA APP PAKAI PLAYWRIGHT MCP\n\nUntuk SETIAP testcase bertipe UI, LANGSUNG buka browser dan interaksi dengan app:\n\n### Flow Per UI Testcase:\n\nStep 1 — BUKA HALAMAN:\n- mcp_playwright_browser_navigate ke URL halaman\n- mcp_playwright_browser_wait_for tunggu halaman loaded\n- mcp_playwright_browser_take_screenshot simpan {TC-ID}-step-1-page-loaded.png\n\nStep 2 — IDENTIFIKASI ELEMEN:\n- mcp_playwright_browser_snapshot untuk lihat semua elemen\n- Catat ref dari setiap elemen yang perlu diinteraksi\n- mcp_playwright_browser_take_screenshot simpan {TC-ID}-step-2-elements.png\n\nStep 3 — ISI FORM FIELD PER FIELD:\n- Untuk SETIAP input field:\n  a. mcp_playwright_browser_click pada field (ref dari snapshot)\n  b. mcp_playwright_browser_type dengan test data\n  c. mcp_playwright_browser_take_screenshot simpan {TC-ID}-step-3{huruf}-fill-{nama-field}.png\n- Setelah SEMUA field terisi:\n  d. mcp_playwright_browser_take_screenshot simpan {TC-ID}-step-3-all-filled.png\n\nStep 4 — KLIK SUBMIT/ACTION:\n- mcp_playwright_browser_click pada button submit/save/create\n- mcp_playwright_browser_wait_for tunggu response\n- mcp_playwright_browser_take_screenshot simpan {TC-ID}-step-4-after-action.png\n\nStep 5 — VERIFIKASI HASIL DI UI:\n- mcp_playwright_browser_snapshot cek DOM state\n- mcp_playwright_browser_evaluate cek success message, data baru, console errors\n- mcp_playwright_browser_take_screenshot simpan {TC-ID}-step-5-verified.png\n\nStep 6 — VERIFIKASI DATA PERSISTED:\n- mcp_playwright_browser_navigate ke halaman list/detail\n- mcp_playwright_browser_wait_for tunggu data muncul\n- mcp_playwright_browser_take_screenshot simpan {TC-ID}-step-6-data-persisted.png\n- ATAU fetch GET ke API untuk cross-check data di backend\n\n### Contoh UI — Login:\n1. navigate ke /login lalu screenshot step-1-login-page.png\n2. snapshot identifikasi fields\n3. Klik email field, type test@example.com, screenshot step-3a-email.png\n4. Klik password field, type testdata, screenshot step-3b-password.png\n5. Screenshot step-3-form-complete.png\n6. Klik Login, wait_for Dashboard, screenshot step-4-logged-in.png\n7. Evaluate cek URL/title, screenshot step-5-dashboard.png\n\n### Contoh UI — CRUD Create:\n1. navigate ke /items, screenshot step-1-list.png\n2. Klik Add New, screenshot step-2-create-form.png\n3. Isi nama, screenshot step-3a-nama.png\n4. Isi deskripsi, screenshot step-3b-deskripsi.png\n5. Isi harga, screenshot step-3c-harga.png\n6. Screenshot step-3-form-complete.png\n7. Klik Save, wait_for success, screenshot step-4-saved.png\n8. Navigate ke list, screenshot step-5-item-in-list.png\n9. Klik item baru, screenshot step-6-detail.png\n\n### Contoh UI — CRUD Edit:\n1. Navigate ke detail item, screenshot step-1-detail.png\n2. Klik Edit, screenshot step-2-edit-form.png\n3. Ubah fields, screenshot per field\n4. Klik Update, wait_for, screenshot step-4-updated.png\n5. Verifikasi perubahan, screenshot step-5-verified.png\n\n### Contoh UI — CRUD Delete:\n1. Navigate ke list, screenshot step-1-list.png\n2. Klik Delete, screenshot step-2-confirm-dialog.png\n3. Klik Confirm, wait_for, screenshot step-3-deleted.png\n4. Verifikasi item hilang, screenshot step-4-removed.png\n\n### Error Path UI:\n- Submit form KOSONG, screenshot validation errors\n- Submit data INVALID, screenshot error per field\n- Akses protected page tanpa login, screenshot redirect/403\n- SETIAP error WAJIB screenshot yang menunjukkan error message JELAS\n\n## BAGIAN C: INTEGRATION TEST — BACKEND + FRONTEND\n\n1. Buat data via UI (Playwright) lalu verifikasi via API (Fetch) — data konsisten\n2. Buat data via API (Fetch) lalu verifikasi muncul di UI (Playwright) — screenshot bukti\n3. Update via UI lalu cek via API — response match\n4. Delete via API lalu refresh UI — screenshot data hilang\n\n## GENERATE 3 REPORT FILES\n\n### A. Markdown: reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/{feature-name}-report.md\n- Summary: total (API + UI + Integration), passed, failed, skipped, blocked, pass rate\n- Section Backend API Tests: per endpoint, request/response, status\n- Section Frontend UI Tests: per flow, step-by-step dengan screenshot references\n- Section Integration Tests: cross-check results\n- Failed analysis + suggestion\n\n### B. HTML: reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/{feature-name}-report.html\n- Dashboard (PASS=hijau, FAIL=merah, SKIP=abu, BLOCKED=oranye)\n- Progress bar pass rate\n- Tab/section Backend API dan Frontend UI\n- Collapsible testcase sections (JS toggle)\n- EMBEDDED SCREENSHOTS INLINE untuk setiap UI step\n- Styled JSON blocks untuk API request/response\n- Error box + suggestion box\n\n### C. JSON: reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/{feature-name}-results.json\n- summary, backend_tests, frontend_tests, integration_tests, failed_analysis\n\n## 10 ATURAN WAJIB\n\n1. HARUS BENAR-BENAR panggil mcp_playwright_browser_* dan fetch — bukan tulis instruksi\n2. SETIAP UI step HARUS screenshot via mcp_playwright_browser_take_screenshot\n3. SETIAP API call HARUS simpan request.json + response.json\n4. mcp_playwright_browser_wait_for SEBELUM setiap screenshot\n5. mcp_playwright_browser_snapshot untuk identifikasi elemen sebelum interact\n6. Form: isi SETIAP field satu per satu, screenshot PER FIELD\n7. Button: klik, tunggu response, screenshot HASIL\n8. Verifikasi: evaluate DOM + screenshot bukti\n9. Error path: test juga, screenshot error messages\n10. SEMUA screenshots dan API captures di-embed di HTML report"
  }
}